                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2_24" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p>Yes. All of our engineers are professional, experienced central heating engineers with
                                        a Gas Safe certification, so you can rest assured you’re getting the most professional
                                        service at a fraction of the cost of other providers.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default  faq-section-panels">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_25" class="btn-accordion collapsed">
                                        Will my new boiler installation make a mess in my home?
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2_25" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p>No. Our engineers always make sure that surfaces are protected and the area they're working
                                        on is always clean and tidy. They always tidy away their working area and do their
                                        utmost to avoid any inconvenience to your home. </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default  faq-section-panels">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_26" class="btn-accordion collapsed">
                                        Do I need to do anything before the engineer arrives?
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2_26" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p>Before your installer arrives, clear away any clutter around the boiler – especially
                                        any valuables and things that could potentially break. Please make sure the boiler
                                        is easy to access and the area is free of items that could cause our engineer delays.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <h3>After Installation</h3>
                        <div class="panel panel-default  faq-section-panels">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_27" class="btn-accordion collapsed">
                                        How do I keep my boiler warranty?
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2_27" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p> Your boiler warranty will only be valid if you have a boiler service regularly. This
                                        usually consists of having a boiler service at least once a year. 24|7 Staywarm also
                                        offer boiler services to homeowners, tenants and landlords as part of our offering.
                                        Please contact our customer service team to find out more.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default faq-section-panels">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_28" class="btn-accordion collapsed">
                                        What exactly does my boiler warranty cover?
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2_28" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p> With most standard new items, you will be offered a one-year warranty. The 24|7 Staywarm
                                        warranty includes everything that has been supplied to you as part of your new installation
                                        and includes the boiler, flue and any attachments, unless you have specifically requested
                                        any of these items not to be included.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default faq-section-panels">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_29" class="btn-accordion collapsed">
                                        Do I need to do anything in order to activate my warranty?
                                    </a>
                                </h4>
                            </div>
                            <div id="collapse2_29" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                                <div class="panel-body">
                                    <p>No. We'll register you with the manufacturer as soon as your engineer fits the boiler.
                                        Then, you'll be covered with your warranty from the moment your boiler is up and
                                        running.
                                    </p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="panel panel-default faq-section-panels">
                            <div class="panel-heading">
                                <h4 class="panel-title">
                                    <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse2_30" class="btn-accordion collapsed">
